      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a> * ProDeo</b>\n</p><p><b>ProDeo</b>, (Pro Deo)<br />\na free version of the former commercial Rebel chess program series by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a> with a complete rewritten personality setting in self-explainable natural language, making it one of the most tunable chess engines. ProDeo is <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant and runs under <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> with various <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUIs</a>, and incorporates an open source <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Encyclopaedia_of_Chess_Openings\">EOC</a> <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">database</a>. ProDeo played the <a href=\"/DOCCC_2004\" title=\"DOCCC 2004\">DOCCC 2004</a>, <a href=\"/ICT_2005\" title=\"ICT 2005\">ICT 2005</a>, <a href=\"/DOCCC_2005\" title=\"DOCCC 2005\">DOCCC 2005</a>, <a href=\"/DOCCC_2011\" title=\"DOCCC 2011\">DOCCC 2011</a>, and the <a href=\"/ICT_2012\" title=\"ICT 2012\">ICT 2012</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Releases\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Releases</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Rating\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rating</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/DOCCC_2004\" title=\"DOCCC 2004\">DOCCC 2004</a>, round 4, <a href=\"/Diep\" title=\"Diep\">Diep</a> - <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ProDeo</a> \n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"DOCCC 2004\"]\n[Site \"Leiden NED\"]\n[Date \"2004.10.17\"]\n[Round \"04\"]\n[White \"Diep\"]\n[Black \"ProDeo\"]\n[Result \"0-1\"]\n\n1.d4 d5 2.c4 c6 3.cxd5 cxd5 4.Nc3 Nf6 5.Nf3 Nc6 6.Bf4 Bf5 7.e3 e6 8.Bb5 Nd7\n9.O-O Be7 10.Rc1 O-O 11.a3 Rc8 12.Be2 Nb6 13.Re1 a6 14.b4 Bd6 15.Bxd6 Qxd6\n16.Nh4 Be4 17.Qb3 Rc7 18.f3 Bg6 19.Red1 Bh5 20.g4 Qe7 21.Ng2 Bg6 22.Kf2 Rfc8 \n23.h4 h6 24.Qb2 Na7 25.g5 hxg5 26.hxg5 Qxg5 27.Qa1 Nb5 28.Nxb5 axb5 29.Rc5 \nNc4 30.Rxc7 Rxc7 31.Rh1 Nd2 32.Rh3 Bb1 33.a4 Rc2 34.Nf4 Rc1 35.Rg3 Qh4 36.axb5 \nNf1 37.Bxf1 Rxf1+ 38.Kxf1 Qxg3 39.Ke2 Qh2+ 40.Kd1 Bf5 41.Qa8+ Kh7 42.Qxb7 Bc2+ \n43.Kc1 Ba4 44.Qc7 Qg1+ 45.Kb2 Qxe3 46.b6 Qd2+ 47.Ka3 Bb5 48.Nh5 Qxd4 49.Qc2+ \nKh6 50.b7 Qa1+ 51.Qa2 Qc3+ 52.Qb3 Qc7 0-1\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20140330071734/http://www.top-5000.nl/prodeo188.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Prodeoinarena.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/71/Prodeoinarena.jpg\" width=\"732\" height=\"396\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ProDeo</a> vs. <a href=\"/Delfi\" title=\"Delfi\">Delfi</a> inside the <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=380502\">Which style is best for ProDeo 1.0&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Norman_Pollock&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Norman Pollock (page does not exist)\">Norm Pollock</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=381935\">ProDeo: what is Chess Knowledge?</a> by Telmo C. Escobar, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 12, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=409080\">ProDeo 1.1 available!</a> by F. Huber, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=429859\">Excellent performance of ProDeo at Leiden...</a> by <a href=\"/Peter_Skinner\" title=\"Peter Skinner\">Peter Skinner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 05, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/ICT_2005\" title=\"ICT 2005\">ICT 2005</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13436\">Pro Deo 1.2 utilities</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2007 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14332\">Pro Deo 1.5</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 07, 2007 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39858\">Pro Deo 1.6 grandmaster personalities</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Dahlem&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David Dahlem (page does not exist)\">David Dahlem</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50546\">ProDeo 1.87 released</a> by Thomas J. Miller, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51092\">ProDeo 1.88 - the let's check version</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 28, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=59317\">ProDeo YAT</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59435\">REBEL | ProDeo book available in Polyglot format</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a>, <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61366\">Ideas</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61529\">ProDeo 2.2 SMP</a> by Damir, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2016 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63658\">ProDeo 2.3 [the BUDDY version]</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=64547\">ProDeo 2.4 - [the ELO version]</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68143\">ProDeo 2.8</a> by Damir, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 06, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69274\">ProDeo 2.9 -- UPDATE --</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69620\">ProDeo 2.91 [another, but last update]</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ProDeo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t2-prodeo-3-0\">ProDeo 3.0</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schroder</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, November 17, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75848\">ProDeo 3.0 has Arrived!</a> by <a href=\"/Ted_Summers\" title=\"Ted Summers\">AdminX</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 17, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t274-prodeo-3-1-the-pesto-version\">ProDeo 3.1 - The PESTO version</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, February 19, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/PeSTO%27s_Evaluation_Function\" title=\"PeSTO&#39;s Evaluation Function\">PeSTO's Evaluation Function</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76643\">ProDeo 3.1 - The PESTO version</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2021 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bra